# RHDP Skills Marketplace - Code Owners
#
# Each plugin has designated owners who must approve changes.
# Changes to a plugin directory require approval from at least one owner.
#
# Format: path/to/directory @github-username @github-username
#
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

